about.facts.1.value: I love traveling. If I'm free, I'm probably on the road.

about.facts.2.value: I prefer camping. Nature is where I feel at peace.

about.facts.3.value: I can eat a lot of ice-cream. And watermelon.

about.facts.4.value: I consider myself an introvert. Talking about myself is hard, so imagine how much time it takes me to write this.

about.facts.5.value: Sun and sea are my best friends.

about.facts.6.value: I do yoga and I try to be regular in my meditations.

about.facts.7.value: Little Eagle is my nickname because my surname in Croatian means just that! :)

about.text.1.value: By a degree, psychologist, by heart, a photographer. Based in Zagreb - Croatia, but available worldwide.

about.text.2.value: I don’t like to be in front of the camera, but I love being the person behind it. Capturing special moments and creating unforgettable memories gives me the feeling of excitement and fills me with joy.

about.text.3.value: I am constantly learning and improving my skills through various workshops and photography courses. With my style evolving, I am open to different ideas and projects.

about.text.4.value: If you have an idea, wish or a vision, feel free to get in touch.

collaborations.text.1.value: In modern times, most of businesses depend on their presentation in the digital world. That includes well-designed websites and social networks, and they are always accompanied by professional photos.

collaborations.text.2.value: I am here to creatively present Your product, idea, You or something else that requires hiring a photographer.

description.value: Little Eagle Photography (Ana Orlić) is an event and portrait photographer from Zagreb, Croatia. Available worldwide.

events.text.1.value: A concert, a dance competition, or a bachelorette party... Whatever event you have in Your near or distant future, I’ll be happy to record it.

events.text.2.value: Professional photos always look good and you can use them for social networks, various posts or simply - memories. ;)

family.text.1.value: The opportunity to capture precious moments in the life of a family is one of my favorite photographic adventures. It involves a lot of spontaneity, love, hugs, and playfulness that kids bring into the story, and that’s always fun! ☺

family.text.2.value: Changes happen quickly, children grow up even faster, pregnancy lasts only for a short time, so the opportunity to forever preserve the memories of one period has a special charm.

home.about.text.1.value: By degree a psychologist, by heart a photographer. Based in Zagreb (Croatia), available worldwide.

home.about.text.2.value: I don’t like to be in front of the camera, but I love being the person behind it. Capturing special moments and creating unforgettable memories gives me the feeling of excitement and fills me with joy.

home.testimonials.anja.value: I had my session at Ana's place 6 months ago and I'm still under the impression. Apart from receiving excellent photos, I had so much fun during the session. Ana was also kind and patient with all my extra requests. Thank you Ana for making me fall in love with myself through your photos.

home.testimonials.bovani.value: It was such a pleasure to work with you for my office photos! You're so pleasant to be around, and helped making me more comfortable in front of the camera, which is never easy for me. Thank you, I can't wait for new photo opportunities in the future!

home.testimonials.lucija.value: We are thrilled. Thank you very much for the effort and the whole agreement, fullfilment of our wishes and fast delivery. You have our recommendation! :)

home.testimonials.nikolina.value: Everybody wants to know who took our wedding photos - and we proudly and gratefully say Little Eagle. So cool, so professional, yet spontaneous and relaxed, just the way it should be. You have our recommendations - because you see all the details, and the details make the difference. ;)

portraits.text.1.value: When it comes to portraits, it is important to me that I understand the person I am photographing and present them at their best. I believe that every person is beautiful and unique and that their personality can be seen through a photo.

portraits.text.2.value: Whatever the reason for taking photos, I'm here to reach the desired goal together. ☺

travels.text.1.value: Traveling is my way of spending my free time, but also my working time. I will often edit my photos in various locations. My office is sometimes a hammock, a bench, a tent, or a coffee shop and that’s what I love about my job.

travels.text.2.value: But I also love carefree travel, when I don’t have to do anything, but I want see everything. Not all trips are recorded with a camera, because sometimes I want to be completely free, but the ones that are documented, you can find below.

weddings.text.1.value: Capturing the love that happens on the wedding day, not only between the newlyweds, but also between family, friends and different generations, is a special responsibility that I readily take on as a photographer. It is important to me to record all of the emotions that are happening that day, as well as the energy that is always unique and unrepeatable.

weddings.text.2.value: I think both, the newlyweds and the photographer, need to click and understand each other’s desires and needs. I’m here for all the questions and concerns, Below you can take a look at some of my weddings so far and see if that’s what you’re looking for for your special day! ☺
